ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would highly recommend the seminar series to all students of chemistry, especially graduate students and upper level undergrads interested in research.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Get to know what other scientists are doing around the country. Sometimes it is really fun when the guest speaker does something that happens to be my interest.
The seminar series helped to expand my knowledge of chemistry by exposing me to new and exciting research in organic groups from around the globe.
It offers a variety of topics that are of my interest and helps me to deepen my overall understanding in some topics.
